name: The Unknowns Saga vol 1: Seki Invasion
name_original: The Unknowns Saga vol 1: Seki Invasion
description:
Seki, Dayo and Evea force to make an unexpected escape crash landed on Earth. As they got back on their feet they soon knowest that each landed on a different part of the world. Now they must try to find the missing starship, get everyone together, and leave Earth before Contour and Moto army declare war on earth.
